{"title":"引言与理论假设","markdown":{"headingText":"引言与理论假设","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n## 研究背景\n资本结构决策是公司金融领域的核心议题。Modigliani & Miller (1958) 的无税完美市场命题之后，学者们从税收、破产成本、信息不对称等摩擦出发，发展出多种理论。其中最具影响力的两大流派分别是：\n\n- **权衡理论 (Trade-off Theory)**：企业在债务税盾收益与财务困境成本之间权衡，认为盈利能力强的企业偿债能力强、税盾价值高，因此应当更多使用债务，即盈利性与杠杆率**正相关**。\n- **优序融资理论 (Pecking Order Theory)**：由于信息不对称，企业融资存在明确的优先序：内源融资 > 债务融资 > 股权融资。盈利能力越强，内源资金越充裕，对外部债务的需求越低，即盈利性与杠杆率**负相关**。\n\n## 研究问题\n本报告利用A股上市公司数据，通过面板数据模型回答以下问题：\n\n1. 中国上市公司整体上更支持哪一种资本结构理论？\n2. 产权性质（国有 vs 民营）是否调节盈利‑杠杆关系？\n3. 这种关系是否随时间变化？是否受宏观经济政策影响？\n4. 企业规模是否构成异质性的来源？\n\n## 文章结构\n后续章节安排如下：第2章介绍数据来源、变量构造与样本筛选；第3章给出核心实证结果；第4章进行稳健性检验（时变系数、规模异质性、门槛效应等）；第5章总结全文并讨论政策启示。","srcMarkdownNoYaml":""},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":true,"code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":false,"preserve-yaml":false,"latex-auto-mk":true,"latex-auto-install":true,"latex-clean":true,"latex-min-runs":1,"latex-max-runs":10,"latex-makeindex":"makeindex","latex-makeindex-opts":[],"latex-tlmgr-opts":[],"latex-input-paths":[],"latex-output-dir":null,"link-external-icon":false,"link-external-newwindow":false,"self-contained-math":false,"format-resources":[],"notebook-links":true},"pandoc":{"standalone":true